title: One of Our Probes Is Missing
Moonrock
description: A U.S. mission to the moon has brought back a moon rock consisting of what's believed to be raw diamonds. World Securities had been entrusted with the moon rock but it has been lost. Lockwood is dispatched to get it back. But the mission won't be easy. Among other things, Lockwood will need to charter a 747.

title: Live Men Tell Tales
description: Probe agent Peter Kubica drowns scuba diving in Dubrovnik. Bianco has the body exhumed which isn't Kubica. Bianco follows the trail to Kubica's mistress in Paris.

title: Operation Iceman
description: The Iceman assassin murders a Probe agent, then threatens a gangster turned ambassador. Bianco forms a team with three other Probe agents to stop the Iceman.

title: The Bullet
description: Lockwood is sent to recover an East German defector who has invented a bullet with a poison jacket. In the process Lockwood is shot and must find the antidote.

title: In Search of Midas
description: C.R. Grover teams with gossip columnist Kate Dawes to verify a rich recluse is still alive who hasn't been seen for eighteen months.

title: The Adonis File
description: The executive secretary to a talk show host is kidnapped. Lockwood is called in to act as intermediary to the kidnappers.

title: Flight to Nowhere
description: A friend of Lockwood who runs an air cargo business disappears on a flight in the desert near Reno, Nevada.
